column1: # Each entry in the table below appears as one point in figure 6D of
# Gene = gene name as provided by wormbase
# siWt = number of reads antisense to and overlapping exons of the
#      indicated gene from a wt adult library.  Read counts are
#      normalized to the number of times each sequence perfectly
# siPrg1 = number of reads antisense to and overlapping exons of the
#      indicated gene from a prg-1 mutant adult library.  Read counts
#      are normalized to the number of times each sequence perfectly
# siWtNorm = siWt divided by total reads in the wt library.
# siPrg1Norm = siPrg1 divided by total reads in the prg-1 mutant library.
# array_change = median signal change for array probes whose Affymetrix-defined
#      coordinate overlap exons of the indicated gene (mutant signal / wt signal).
